<html>
  <head>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Lato:ital,wght@0,100;0,300;0,400;0,700;0,900;1,100;1,300;1,400;1,700;1,900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  </head>
  <body class="w-full flex flex-col items-center leading-relaxed">
    <main>
      <div class="w-full max-w-2xl pt-10 flex flex-col gap-9">
        <h1 class="text-2xl tracking-wide m-0">Ben Isenstein</h1>
        <section class="flex flex-col gap-5">
          <p class="p-0 m-0">I'm a full stack developer. I love crafting rich experiences for the web. I think <span class="italic">the web platform itself</span> is one of the coolest things there is, and I like to enable other devs and businesses to build for the web more effectively.</p>
          <p class="p-0 m-0">I live in Calgary, Alberta, Canada. I travel throughout the Americas to visit friends, climb mountains, dance, and play music.</p>
          <p class="p-0 m-0">I spent four years as a musician, completing a bachelors degree in jazz piano. Now I bring a sense of deep observation, creativity, and collaboration to my work in tech.</p>
          <p class="p-0 m-0">I regularly conduct talks and "ask-me-anythings" at <a class="font-bold text-black" href="https://www.inceptionu.com/" target="_blank">InceptionU</a>, my alma mater bootcamp in Calgary. Growing up, I often found myself in environments where direct mentorship was plentiful. Music teachers, coaches, summer camp leaders - I believe giving and receiving mentorship makes communities, organizations and teams much stronger.</p>
          <p class="p-0 m-0">I consulted full-time for Canadian pension <a class="font-bold text-black" href="https://www.omers.com/" target="_blank">OMERS</a> via agency <a class="font-bold text-black" href="https://www.devtheory.com/" target="_blank">DevTheory</a> from 2022-2024.</p>
          <p class="p-0 m-0">I'm currently nomadic in South America.</p>
        </section>
        <section>
          <h2 class="p-0 m-0 mb-4 text-lg">Tech and tools I work with:</h2>
          <div class="w-full max-w-2xl flex flex-wrap gap-y-4">
            <div class="w-144px">
              <h3 class="p-0 m-0 text-base italic font-bold text-stone-500">
                Languages
              </h3>
              <ul class="pl-4 m-0">
                <li>HTML</li>
                <li>CSS</li>
                <li>TypeScript</li>
                <li>Python</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="w-144px">
              <h3 class="p-0 m-0 text-base italic font-bold text-stone-500">
                Local Dev
              </h3>
              <ul class="pl-4 m-0">
                <li>VS Code</li>
                <li>NodeJS</li>
                <li>Vite</li>
                <li>Docker</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="w-144px">
              <h3 class="p-0 m-0 text-base italic font-bold text-stone-500">
                Infra
              </h3>
              <ul class="pl-4 m-0">
                <li>Railway</li>
                <li>Azure</li>
                <li>Google Cloud</li>
                <li>Github</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="w-144px">
              <h3 class="p-0 m-0 text-base italic font-bold text-stone-500">
                Storage
              </h3>
              <ul class="pl-4 m-0">
                <li>SQLite</li>
                <li>Postgres</li>
                <li>MongoDB</li>
                <li>Azure Storage</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="w-144px">
              <h3 class="p-0 m-0 text-base italic font-bold text-stone-500">
                Backend
              </h3>
              <ul class="pl-4 m-0">
                <li>Express</li>
                <li>Flask</li>
                <li>Supabase</li>
                <li>Serverless</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="w-144px">
              <h3 class="p-0 m-0 text-base italic font-bold text-stone-500">
                Frontend
              </h3>
              <ul class="pl-4 m-0">
                <li>React</li>
                <li>Astro</li>
                <li>Vanilla</li>
                <li>TailwindCSS</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
        <section>
          <h2 class="p-0 m-0 mb-4 text-lg">Connect with me online:</h2>
          <div class="flex gap-2">
            <span class="py-1 px-2 flex items-center bg-stone-200 rounded-md">
              <span class="text-xl i-logos:github-icon"></span>
              &nbsp;
              <a class="text-black" href="https://github.com/BenIsenstein" target="_blank">Github</a>
            </span>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
